quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,"'idha alsama' anshqt, wakhtll nzamha, wa'iidha alkawakib tsaqtt, wa'iidha albihar fjjar allah bedha fi bed, fdhhb mawha, wa'iidha alqubur qulibt bbeth man kan fyha, hinayidh taelam kll nafs jmye aemalha, ma tqddam mnha, wama takhr, wjwzyt bha"
  82,2,"'idha alsama' anshqt, wakhtll nzamha, wa'iidha alkawakib tsaqtt, wa'iidha albihar fjjar allah bedha fi bed, fdhhb mawha, wa'iidha alqubur qulibt bbeth man kan fyha, hinayidh taelam kll nafs jmye aemalha, ma tqddam mnha, wama takhr, wjwzyt bha"
  82,3,"'idha alsama' anshqt, wakhtll nzamha, wa'iidha alkawakib tsaqtt, wa'iidha albihar fjjar allah bedha fi bed, fdhhb mawha, wa'iidha alqubur qulibt bbeth man kan fyha, hinayidh taelam kll nafs jmye aemalha, ma tqddam mnha, wama takhr, wjwzyt bha"
  82,4,"'idha alsama' anshqt, wakhtll nzamha, wa'iidha alkawakib tsaqtt, wa'iidha albihar fjjar allah bedha fi bed, fdhhb mawha, wa'iidha alqubur qulibt bbeth man kan fyha, hinayidh taelam kll nafs jmye aemalha, ma tqddam mnha, wama takhr, wjwzyt bha"
  82,5,"'iidha alsama' anshqt, wakhtll nzamha, wa'iidha alkawakib tsaqtt, wa'iidha albihar fjjar allah bedha fi bed, fdhhb mawha, wa'iidha alqubur qulibt bbeth man kan fyha, hinayidh taelam kll nafs jmye aemalha, ma tqddam mnha, wama takhr, wjwzyt bha"
  82,6,"ya 'ayuha al'iinsan almunkar llbeth, ma aldhy jelk tghtarr birabik aljwad kthyr alkhayr alhqyq balshkr waltaet, 'alays hu aladhi khalaqak fswwa khalaqak feadalk, wrkkabk li'ada' wzayfk, fi ay surat sha'ha khlqk?"
  82,7,"ya 'ayuha al'iinsan almunkar llbeth, ma aldhy jelk tghtarr birabik aljwad kthyr alkhayr alhqyq balshkr waltaet, 'alays hu aladhi khalaqak fswwa khalaqak feadalk, wrkkabk li'ada' wzayfk, fi ay surat sha'ha khlqk?"
  82,8,"ya 'ayuha al'iinsan almunkar llbeth, ma aldhy jelk tghtarr birabik aljwad kthyr alkhayr alhqyq balshkr waltaet, 'alays hu aladhi khalaqak fswwa khalaqak feadalk, wrkkabk li'ada' wzayfk, fi ay surat sha'ha khlqk?"
  82,9,"lys al'amr kama taqulun min 'anakum fi eibadatikum ghayr allah muhiqwn, bal tkdhdhibwn biawm alhisab waljza'. wa'iina ealaykum lmlaykt rqba' kiramana ealaa allah katibin lamaa wukkilu b'ihsayh, la yfwthm min 'aemalikum wasrarkm shy', yaelamun ma tafealun min khayr 'aw shr"
  82,10,"lys al'amr kama taqulun min 'anakum fi eibadatikum ghayr allah muhiqwn, bal tkdhdhibwn biawm alhisab waljza'. wa'iina ealaykum lmlaykt rqba' kiramana ealaa allah katibin lamaa wukkilu b'ihsayh, la yfwthm min 'aemalikum wasrarkm shy', yaelamun ma tafealun min khayr 'aw shr"
  82,11,"lys al'amr kama taqulun min 'anakum fi eibadatikum ghayr allah muhiqwn, bal tkdhdhibwn biawm alhisab waljza'. wa'iina ealaykum lmlaykt rqba' kiramana ealaa allah katibin lamaa wukkilu b'ihsayh, la yfwthm min 'aemalikum wasrarkm shy', yaelamun ma tafealun min khayr 'aw shr"
  82,12,"lays al'amr kama taqulun min 'anakum fi eibadatikum ghayr allah muhiqwn, bal tkdhdhibwn biawm alhisab waljza'. wa'iina ealaykum lmlaykt rqba' kiramana ealaa allah katibin lamaa wukkilu b'ihsayh, la yfwthm min 'aemalikum wasrarkm shy', yaelamun ma tafealun min khayr 'aw shr"
  82,13,'in alatqya' alqaymyn bihuquq allah wahuquq eibadih lafi neym
  82,14,"w'in alfujjar aladhin qassaru fi huquq allah wahuquq eibadih lafi jhym, yusibahum lhbha yawm aljza', wama hum ean eadhab jahanam bighayibin la bkhrwj wala bmwt"
  82,15,"w'in alfujjar aladhin qassaru fi huquq allah wahuquq eibadih lafi jhym, yusibahum lhbha yawm aljza', wama hum ean eadhab jahanam bighayibin la bkhrwj wala bmwt"
  82,16,"w'in alfujjar aladhin qassaru fi huquq allah wahuquq eibadih lafi jhym, yusibahum lhbha yawm aljza', wama hum ean eadhab jahanam bighayibin la bkhrwj wala bmwt"
  82,17,"wma 'adrak ma ezmt yawm alhsab, thuma ma 'adrak ma ezmt yawm alhsab? yawm alhisab la yuqadar ahd ealaa nfe ahd, wal'amr fi dhalik alyawm lilah wahdah aldhy la yghlbh ghalb, wala yqhrh qahr, wala ynazeh ahd"
  82,18,"wma 'adrak ma ezmt yawm alhsab, thuma ma 'adrak ma ezmt yawm alhsab? yawm alhisab la yuqadar ahd ealaa nfe ahd, wal'amr fi dhalik alyawm lilah wahdah aldhy la yghlbh ghalb, wala yqhrh qahr, wala ynazeh ahd"
  82,19,"wma 'adrak ma ezmt yawm alhsab, thuma ma 'adrak ma ezmt yawm alhsab? yawm alhisab la yuqadar ahd ealaa nfe ahd, wal'amr fi dhalik alyawm lilah wahdah aldhy la yghlbh ghalb, wala yqhrh qahr, wala ynazeh ahd"
  83,1,"edhab shadid liladhin yubkhasun almikyal walmyzan, aladhin 'iidha ashtarawa min alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yufun lanfshm, wa'iidha baeu alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yunqswn fi almikyal walmyzan, fkyf bihal min ysrqhma wykhtlshma, wybkhs alnaas ashya'hm? 'iinah 'uwlaa bialwaeid min mtffy almikyal walmyzan. 'alaa yaetaqid 'uwlayik almtffwn 'ana allah taealaa baethhm wmhasbhm ealaa 'aemalihim fi yawm eazim alhwl? yawm yaqum alnaas bayn yaday allh, fyhasbhm ealaa alqlyl walkthyr, wahum fih khadewn lilah rabi alealmyn"
  83,2,"edhab shadid liladhin yubkhasun almikyal walmyzan, aladhin 'iidha ashtarawa min alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yufun lanfshm, wa'iidha baeu alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yunqswn fi almikyal walmyzan, fkyf bihal min ysrqhma wykhtlshma, wybkhs alnaas ashya'hm? 'iinah 'uwlaa bialwaeid min mtffy almikyal walmyzan. 'alaa yaetaqid 'uwlayik almtffwn 'ana allah taealaa baethhm wmhasbhm ealaa 'aemalihim fi yawm eazim alhwl? yawm yaqum alnaas bayn yaday allh, fyhasbhm ealaa alqlyl walkthyr, wahum fih khadewn lilah rabi alealmyn"
  83,3,"edhab shadid liladhin yubkhasun almikyal walmyzan, aladhin 'iidha ashtarawa min alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yufun lanfshm, wa'iidha baeu alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yunqswn fi almikyal walmyzan, fkyf bihal min ysrqhma wykhtlshma, wybkhs alnaas ashya'hm? 'iinah 'uwlaa bialwaeid min mtffy almikyal walmyzan. 'alaa yaetaqid 'uwlayik almtffwn 'ana allah taealaa baethhm wmhasbhm ealaa 'aemalihim fi yawm eazim alhwl? yawm yaqum alnaas bayn yaday allh, fyhasbhm ealaa alqlyl walkthyr, wahum fih khadewn lilah rabi alealmyn"
  83,4,"edhab shadid liladhin yubkhasun almikyal walmyzan, aladhin 'iidha ashtarawa min alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yufun lanfshm, wa'iidha baeu alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yunqswn fi almikyal walmyzan, fkyf bihal min ysrqhma wykhtlshma, wybkhs alnaas ashya'hm? 'iinah 'uwlaa bialwaeid min mtffy almikyal walmyzan. 'alaa yaetaqid 'uwlayik almtffwn 'ana allah taealaa baethhm wmhasbhm ealaa 'aemalihim fi yawm eazim alhwl? yawm yaqum alnaas bayn yaday allh, fyhasbhm ealaa alqlyl walkthyr, wahum fih khadewn lilah rabi alealmyn"
  83,5,"edhab shadid liladhin yubkhasun almikyal walmyzan, aladhin 'iidha ashtarawa min alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yufun lanfshm, wa'iidha baeu alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yunqswn fi almikyal walmyzan, fkyf bihal min ysrqhma wykhtlshma, wybkhs alnaas ashya'hm? 'iinah 'uwlaa bialwaeid min mtffy almikyal walmyzan. 'alaa yaetaqid 'uwlayik almtffwn 'ana allah taealaa baethhm wmhasbhm ealaa 'aemalihim fi yawm eazim alhwl? yawm yaqum alnaas bayn yaday allh, fyhasbhm ealaa alqlyl walkthyr, wahum fih khadewn lilah rabi alealmyn"
  83,6,"edhab shadid liladhin yubkhasun almikyal walmyzan, aladhin 'iidha ashtarawa min alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yufun lanfshm, wa'iidha baeu alnaas mkyla 'aw mwzwnana yunqswn fi almikyal walmyzan, fkyf bihal min ysrqhma wykhtlshma, wybkhs alnaas ashya'hm? 'iinah 'uwlaa bialwaeid min mtffy almikyal walmyzan. 'alaa yaetaqid 'uwlayik almtffwn 'ana allah taealaa baethhm wmhasbhm ealaa 'aemalihim fi yawm eazim alhwl? yawm yaqum alnaas bayn yaday allh, fyhasbhm ealaa alqlyl walkthyr, wahum fih khadewn lilah rabi alealmyn"
  83,7,"hqa 'iina masir alfujjar wamawahum lafi dyq, wama 'adrak ma hdha aldyq? 'iinah sijn muqim waeadhab alym, wahu ma kutib lahum almasir 'ilyh, maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs"
  83,8,"haqana 'iina masir alfujjar wamawahum lafi dyq, wama 'adrak ma hdha aldyq? 'iinah sijn muqim waeadhab alym, wahu ma kutib lahum almasir 'ilyh, maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs"
  83,9,"hqa 'iina masir alfujjar wamawahum lafi dyq, wama 'adrak ma hdha aldyq? 'iinah sijn muqim waeadhab alym, wahu ma kutib lahum almasir 'ilyh, maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs"
  83,10,"edhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,11,"edhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,12,"eadhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,13,"edhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,14,"edhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,15,"eadhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,16,"edhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,17,"edhab shadid yawmayidh llmkdhbyn, aladhin yukadhibun biwuque yawm aljza', wama ykdhdhib bih 'iilaa kulu zalim kthyr al'ithm, 'iidha ttla ealayh ayat alquran qal: hadhih abatyl alawlyn. lays al'amr kama zemu, bal hu kalam allah wwhyh 'iilaa nbyh, wa'iinama hjb qulubuhum ean altasdiq bih ma ghshaha min kathrat ma yrtkbwn min aldhnwb. lays al'amr kama zaeam alkfar, bal 'iinahum yawm alqiamat ean ruyat rbhm- jl wela- lmhjwbwn, (wfy hadhih alayat dlalt ealaa ruyat almuminin rbbahm fi aljn) thuma 'iinahum ldakhlw alnaar yqaswn hrha, thuma yuqal lhm: hdha aljaza' aladhi kuntum bih tkdhbwn"
  83,18,"haqana 'iina kitab al'abrar -whm almtqwn- lafi almratb alealiat fi aljn. wama 'adrak -ayha alrswl- ma hadhih almratb alealy? kitab al'abrar maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs, yattalie ealayh almuqarabun min malayikat kl sma'"
  83,19,"hqa 'iina kitab al'abrar -whm almtqwn- lafi almratb alealiat fi aljn. wama 'adrak -ayha alrswl- ma hadhih almratb alealy? kitab al'abrar maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs, yattalie ealayh almuqarabun min malayikat kl sma'"
  83,20,"hqa 'iina kitab al'abrar -whm almtqwn- lafi almratb alealiat fi aljn. wama 'adrak -ayha alrswl- ma hadhih almratb alealy? kitab al'abrar maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs, yattalie ealayh almuqarabun min malayikat kl sma'"
  83,21,"hqa 'iina kitab al'abrar -whm almtqwn- lafi almratb alealiat fi aljn. wama 'adrak -ayha alrswl- ma hadhih almratb alealy? kitab al'abrar maktub mfrwgh mnh, la yzad fih wala yunqs, yattalie ealayh almuqarabun min malayikat kl sma'"
  83,22,"'in 'ahl alsidq waltaet lafi aljanat ytnemwn, ealaa alasrrat yanzurun 'iilaa rbhm, wa'iilaa ma aedd lahum min khyrat, taraa fi wujuhihim bahjat alneym, yusqawn min khamr safyt mhkm 'inawha, akhirah rayihat msk, wafi dhlk alnaeim almuqim flytsabq almtsabqwn. whdha alsharab mzajh wkhlth min eayn fi aljanat tueraf lelwha b \"tsnym\", eayan aedt; lyshrb minha almqrbwn, wytldhdhu bha"
  83,23,"'in 'ahl alsidq waltaet lafi aljanat ytnemwn, ealaa alasrrat yanzurun 'iilaa rbhm, wa'iilaa ma aedd lahum min khyrat, taraa fi wujuhihim bahjat alneym, yusqawn min khamr safyt mhkm 'inawha, akhirah rayihat msk, wafi dhlk alnaeim almuqim flytsabq almtsabqwn. whdha alsharab mzajh wkhlth min eayn fi aljanat tueraf lelwha b \"tsnym\", eayan aedt; lyshrb minha almqrbwn, wytldhdhu bha"
  83,24,"'iina 'ahl alsidq waltaet lafi aljanat ytnemwn, ealaa alasrrat yanzurun 'iilaa rbhm, wa'iilaa ma aedd lahum min khyrat, taraa fi wujuhihim bahjat alneym, yusqawn min khamr safyt mhkm 'inawha, akhirah rayihat msk, wafi dhlk alnaeim almuqim flytsabq almtsabqwn. whdha alsharab mzajh wkhlth min eayn fi aljanat tueraf lelwha b \"tsnym\", eayan aedt; lyshrb minha almqrbwn, wytldhdhu bha"
  83,25,"'in 'ahl alsidq waltaet lafi aljanat ytnemwn, ealaa alasrrat yanzurun 'iilaa rbhm, wa'iilaa ma aedd lahum min khyrat, taraa fi wujuhihim bahjat alneym, yusqawn min khamr safyt mhkm 'inawha, akhirah rayihat msk, wafi dhlk alnaeim almuqim flytsabq almtsabqwn. whdha alsharab mzajh wkhlth min eayn fi aljanat tueraf lelwha b \"tsnym\", eayan aedt; lyshrb minha almqrbwn, wytldhdhu bha"
